#-   In the beginning of     the world, all was      naught for Redberet,  the Fox, and the Bat.

     Redberet had         befriended the Fox
    seeing it's uses
  through it's flaws.

       In the Bat, 
    He saw nothing.
 Just an annoyance
      with no use.
#-        He seeked
  to destroy the Bat,
    but he could not,
 for it kept appearing
     no matter what.

       By this act,
all bats shall be killed
  if seen by they who    follow the Redberet.

