#-  After the creation of
    the First World,           Mankind was in
   a peaceful state.

         No clan
    had been made
     and no rivals
had been constructed.

        The place
     that all people
        come from
 was merely a village-
#-   - and unorganized
         at that.

        This time
    was short lived
         as war
 was soon to blossom
  in the minds of man.
#- 



