         ﾂｧ4 ﾂｧnOf Warﾂｧr
#-    After the people
     had gathered
        into clans
      and factions
      war was only
the natural next step.

   The greatest war
       in this time
   was the UwO war,
 in which a clan called
    OwO was forced
  to rise up against-
#-  - The force of evil            called UwU.

 Even though UwU was    silenced, The effect    the war had on the    world was felt for a        long time after.

   No power was like       that of UwU in the      world, and one shall       not be the same.
