  ﾂｧ2 A Time of Greedﾂｧr
#-  After the age of war,
   a need for money
     arose across
   across the world.

      Greed arose,
   prompting massive
 factories to be made,
       and nations
   to be constructed
        from them.
#-  


The world prospered
    for a short time,
     but eventually
        everyone
 got what they wanted,
    and had no need
    to live in a world
    with nothing to do.
#-    Heed this warning,
 for you shall not fall
 to the dilemma they of
   the first world did.

       They died
     a slow death
 which you shall avoid.

  Keep yourself busy,
      build massive
       structures
       in the name
      of the Beret!
#-      

+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+

      Do not falter
      in your faith,
    for he who does
  is a sure forebear
    of uselessness,
 just as the Bat was.

‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾
#-        


        ﾂｧ4Rules
          of the
            New World

ﾂｧr

   |¥__/|
