#- 
  In this New World,
    you must wear
   upon your head
 a leather hat of red
  when not in combat
 as it will signify you
     as a follower.

    We must dedicate
    ourselves to His
   word, and follow it.

#- 

‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾

       Be merry,
   For if you follow
 the way of Redberet,
      you will have
   everlasting peace.

+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+
