ﾂｧ1

ﾂｧl       Book III ﾂｧr
   Honour in Working


=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=
#-    

   To you who do not
    spread the word,
     feel no regret,
        but pride.

     You, while not
  spreading his word,
   can help fuel his
         Kingdom.
#- 
     You who farm,
   you feed the men
       and women
    that protect us
 and spread the word.

     You who build
   great structures,
 make them in his name,
     and be valiant
   in your creations.
#- 
    You who master
   the art of battle
  and fight his wars,
   protect his name
  and follow his law.

    All who serve Him
   shall follow His law
   and they who help
        interpret
     and enforce it.
#- 

          Listen
 to your governments,
      but also follow
         His rule.

       If man tries
to restrict your belief
    in Him, leave them
and find safe harbour
    in another land.
#- 

+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+‾+

          Even
when you do not work,
       honor Him
      by wearing
  a red leather helm.

